						               													<description>In Top Fantasy one player each round picks a card from the deck, then tries to make the others guess what's shown on this card in the manner indicated on the top card of the deck: using only the hands; using noises and sounds but no words; telling a story about the card; and creating a statue with your body.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All players have only one opportunity to show their guess by placing their finger on what they think is the face-up matching card on the table. If the card is guessed, the active player keeps their card and the one who guessed takes the twin card from the table. If the card is not guessed, the active player places the card under the deck. In both cases, the next player in clockwise order becomes the active player. The first player to collect nine cards wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
